            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><div n="1" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/>
                Pro salute <expan><abbr>Aug</abbr><ex>usti</ex></expan> <lb n="2"/>in honorem <expan><abbr>d</abbr><ex>omus</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>d</abbr><ex>ivinae</ex></expan> Soli <lb n="3"/>Invicto <expan><abbr>Mythr</abbr><ex>ae</ex></expan> <note>sic</note> Hilarus <lb n="4"/><expan><abbr>Aug</abbr><ex>usti</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>lib</abbr><ex>ertus</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>tab</abbr><ex>ularius</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>p</abbr><ex>rocuratoris</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>r</abbr><ex>egni</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>N</abbr><ex>orici</ex></expan> et Epictetus <lb n="5"/><expan><abbr>ark</abbr><ex>arius</ex></expan> <note>sic</note> <expan><abbr>Aug</abbr><ex>usti</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>n</abbr><ex>ostri</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>tem</abbr><ex>plum</ex></expan> vetustate conl<expan><ex>ap</ex><abbr>s</abbr><ex>um</ex></expan> <lb n="6"/>sumptu suo cum pictura refe<supplied reason="lost"><expan><abbr>c</abbr><ex>erunt</ex></expan></supplied> <lb n="7"/><expan><abbr>Imp</abbr><ex>eratore</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>d</abbr><ex>omino</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>n</abbr><ex>ostro</ex></expan> Gordiano <expan><abbr>Aug</abbr><ex>usto</ex></expan> et Aviola c<supplied reason="lost"><expan><abbr>o</abbr><ex>n</ex><abbr>s</abbr><ex>ulibus</ex></expan></supplied> <lb n="8"/><expan><abbr>sacerdot</abbr><ex>e</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Licin</abbr><ex>io</ex></expan> Marcello pat<supplied reason="lost" cert="low">re sac(rorum)</supplied> </ab></div><div n="2" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> <expan><abbr>d</abbr><ex>edicatum</ex></expan> VIII <expan><abbr>K</abbr><ex>alendas</ex></expan> Iulias <expan><abbr>Q</abbr><ex>uinto</ex></expan> Vi<gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/>
            </ab></div></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Material: Marmor aus Kraig. Tafel rechts gebrochen; Erhaltungszustand zur Zeit der Aufnahme durch Mommsen im rechten Bereich noch vollständiger als heute.</p>
